                  "text": "Linear functionals and their relation to linear transformations",
                  "children": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "level": "v",
              "levelType": "lowercase",
              "text": "Inner products and inner product spaces: self-conjugate, or Hermitian, matrices; unitary and orthogonal matrices",
              "children": [
                {
                  "level": "vi",
                  "levelType": "roman",
                  "text": "Linear operators in an inner product space: self-adjoint, or Hermitian, operators; unitary and orthogonal operators; the spectral theorem for normal operators",
                  "children": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "level": "b",
              "levelType": "lowercase",
              "text": "Multilinear algebra",
              "children": []
            }
